Dialogue.Value: It’s a beautiful cyber-cherry tree!
CALM WATER IS FAR MORE,SOOTHING THAN DIRTY OLD,TREES，RIGHT?
FILLED WITH POLLEN AND,INSECTS，ICK! I HEARD THEY,GROW IN DIRT!
THESE TREES ARE MORE,BEAUTIFUL THAN SOME,BORING WATER，RIGHT?
WHO EVEN DRINKS WATER?,AND WHAT DO FISH,EVEN DO IN THERE?
YOU HEAR THAT?!
It is said that all data deleted in,the past gathers around this,tree.
I was close.... so close.... to,finding the ultimate strategy....,becoming the ultimate Navi....!
But in the blink of an eye....,With a single mis-step....,I lost everything....
I have no interest in weaklings,who have sacrificed nothing....,Leave me to my misery....
You think you can succeed,where I had failed....?
I will show you the mistake,you have made....
Are you here to mock me....?
Do you think I am a helpless,victim....? Powerless....?,An easy target...?
I will show you how wrong,you are!
Not that a weakling like you,would understand....
Unless it is now a fashion,statement to leave yourself,at the mercy of viruses....?
Get out of my sight before,I remove you myself....!
Unbelievable....,To have taken my strategy,and perfected it....
THANK YOU FOR SAVING,ME FROM THOSE AWFUL，,AWFUL NAVIS!
WELCOME TO HEAVEN,SQUARE! WE DON’T GET,MANY VISITORS!
I’M THE SPRITE THAT,CONNECTS LINK GATES!
I CAN LINK THIS SQUARE，,SUCH AS IT IS， TO YOUR,HOMEPAGE!
THE CONNECTION FEE IS,45000 ZENNY!
CREATE A LINK?
UNFORTUNATELY，YOU,DON’T HAVE ENOUGH,MONEY!
LINK CREATED!
I HOPE TO SEE YOU AGAIN,SOON!
NORMALLY THIS WHOLE,AREA IS A SAFE PLACE!
BUT SOMETHING HAS,DRIVEN ALL THE SPIRITS,INTO A FRENZY!
JUST WHAT IS THE ,CYBERWORLD COMING TO?
I can move on，freed from my,regrets....!,At last....!
I see now....,With enough skill，true skill....,My strategy holds true....!
To see my own techniques,perfected....!
It’s an old playbook filled to,the brim with battle strategies,and modification plans.
The departed spirit left,something behind....
The final page has been angrily,scratched out，but the number,“11111111” is faintly legible.
It looks like the previous,owner had a habit of using,random items as bookmarks!
We didn’t miss any side paths，,did we，Shanghai?
If there’s nowhere else，then,this has to be the way forward，,but....
....2 million....,....seven，no，eight bounties....?
....Hey，Alice.,Aren’t you tired? A nap right,now seems great，huh?
You’re right，Shanghai，a nap,does sound great，doesn’t it?
But it’s not like we can stay,in bed all day!,Up and at ’em，Shanghai!
Hehe--!,Oops，I knew there was,something I forgot!
Having a bit of trouble?,“Forgot” how to open your,own doors?
Youmu!,Look at what it’s done this time!
The system reports that it,entered lockout after too many,failed access attempts....
The corruption must have,adapted to the automatic filter.
Hey! I made you!,What do you mean “remote,access disabled” ?!
Each barrier holds a fragment,of the Mistress’ power，and,would recognize its owner.
But to bring Mistress Yuyuko,so close to the corruption....,The risks are too great.
Oh，no.,You hear that， Alice? Looks,like there’s nothing we can do.
SCAN COMPLETE,VERIFYING IDENTITY
WELCOME BACK，,MISTRESS OF 144,FORMS OF COMBAT
WELCOME BACK，,MISTRESS YUYUKO
The fragment in the barrier,must have gotten.... confused....,during the scan.
That’s great!,Now we just have to get rid of,all that ugly corruption!
And how would “we” do that?
The barrier absorbs incoming,attacks and uses that power,to charge an internal buffer.
If that buffer can be overloaded，,the resulting purge should be,able to clear the corruption.
Along with the person who was,just shooting it and everything,else nearby，I bet.
Whatever，blowing these things,up is as good a plan as any.,This better be worth it.
Alice，let’s go through our chip,folder one more time and get,this over with.
TITLE NOT FOUND:,MISTRESS OF 144,FORMS OF COMBAT
ACCESS DENIED
What a shame.
See you soon!
See you soon!
Here，let me get those doors,for you!
It’s a tall，multicompartment,cyber-refridgerator.
It chills cyber-food and keeps,it safe from.... cyber.... bacteria?
The air is still warm around the,oven; it seems that somebody,was just using it.
Older，less popular models,needed to use heat-element,chips as fuel.
Spotless tableware and,cutlery are neatly arranged,in organized cabinets.
A tall，firm cushion takes the,place of a chair.
It seems to be a traditional,sitting table，but raised to,standing height.
For NetNavis，cyber-cuisine is,a luxury，so a personal dining,area like this is a rare sight.
I think they’d notice if I tried to,barge into their private room.
Two swords are displayed ,on the shelf，between closets,of assorted supplies.
While most swords used in,battle are battlechips，it seems,these have seen real use.
Knock. Knock.
Oh，it’s you!,Come in，we were just about,to get started!
Isn’t Youmu amazing?,Sit，sit! I can’t wait to dig in!
....and that’s how the White,Heaven Area regulates the,cycle of souls!
Hmph. How about the part,where you needed me to clean,up your own area for you?
Ugh，it’s all because of those,nasty ghosts!
Go on，Youmu!,Tell her what happened!
#b@false#As you wish，Mistress.,#w@150##e#
#b@false#Some time ago，a large mass,of souls came to our garden,after some disaster on the Net.#w@60##e@#
#b@false#Most moved on peacefully....,But among them were groups,of....#w@24# abnormal souls.#w@24##e@#
#b@false#Many times more dense than a,normal Navi，they clung to their,bodies rather than pass on.#w@25##e@#
#b@false#Worse，these....#w@20# abominations,fed on the souls of others，,attacking all in their way.#w@25##e@#
#b@false#What monsters. Wow.,Attacking innocent people....,Takes one to know one，huh?#w@75##e@#
#b@false#Rrrgh--!#p@MCFParallelAngry#,If anything，you--!#w@45#,#p@MCFParallelAngryEnd##e@#
#b@false#As chief administrator of the,area，Mistress Yuyuko was,able to stop the invasion.#w@75##e@#
#b@false#That is，until the last abnormal,soul arrived....#w@120##e@#
#b@false#Not only was it massive，but,the sheer weight of its regrets,warped the world around it.#w@75##e@#
#b@false#The invaders’ seals unravelled,under the pressure，and they,rampaged across the area.#w@120##e@#
#b@false#...Lady Yuyuko had to banish,the soul while we contained,the damage.#w@75##e@#
#b@false#But while we were occupied，a,being of great evil broke in and,spirited away the sealed soul.#w@75##e@#
#b@false#Who knows what she could do,with that soul’s power....#w@75##e@#
Besides be a huge pain in my,neck，you mean?
Just making sure though，,Little Miss Big Bad Evil is the,Queen of Darkness，right?
#b@false#Ahem.#w@25#,Excuse me.#w@25##e@#
The Queen of Darkness....?,Oh，she would just love that!
Don’t mind Youmu，I’m sure,Mima was just popping in to,say hi!
You should visit her!,She’s probably cooped up in,her lair with her new toy.
Oh，where did I put that key....?
Perhaps it slipped out during,the chaos....?
No，wait....,....Aha! Here it is!,How lucky!
You do know there’s a bounty,on her head，right?
Oh，I’m sure she’ll be fine!,She’s just across the way，,tell her I said hi!
My lady.... often sees things,very differently than most.
Do not expect any mercy，or,honor，or reason from that,woman or her.... creations.
You’ll find her lab deep in the,Undernet. Even the Net around,her is barren and lifeless.
Uh-huh.,See ya.
Got that all out of your system，,Shanghai?
#b@false#Now，you better be--!#b@false##w@30##e@#
Mmm!,So good!
Alice，I don’t want to hear it.
Now，there’s no need to be,so rude....
#b@false#What I meant to say，is that the,invaders shared a distinct,spiritual signature.#w@25##e@#
#b@false#When I detected your,metaphysical.... weight....,I assumed the worst.#w@25##e@#
#b@false#As I was saying....#w@25##e@#
#b@false#However，for a time，things,were peaceful.#w@75##e@#
#b@false#But until we could free the souls,they had trapped，we could,only seal the intruders away.#w@75##e@#
#b@false#Faced with spreading chaos,and unchecked corruption，,in order to protect the server....#w@120##e@#
#b@false#However，Lady Yuyuko’s full,power was occupied restraining,the soul and its corruption.#w@75##e@#
#b@false#Without the ability to seal the,invaders，we instead lured and,trapped them within our vaults.#w@150##e@#
Is that....?
Roukanken!,I thought you were lost to the,invaders forever!
Are those stains?! Ugh!,Oh，I’ll take care of you as,soon as I can!
....Ah!,Thank you for recovering my,sword and returning it to me.
In return，I would be willing to,share some techniques，if you,have the patience to learn.
I will be waiting in the side,room，seeing to my blade.
Finally， returned to your rightful,place....
Are you here to test yourself,against my blades?
Challenge Youmu to a,NetBattle?
With the true Roukanken back,in my hands，there is nothing,that can’t be cut!
Perhaps you will be ready,some other time.
I suppose there’s nothing more,I can teach you.
....Here，take this.
While battle data will never,compare to the real thing，I feel,that you could use it properly.
There are few that can stand,against Roukanken and,Hakurouken.
Would you mind a friendly spar?,I feel there is much we could,learn from eachother.
Challenge Youmu to a,NetBattle?
Thank you for the match.,There is much I can do to,improve，it seems.
A fine attempt，however.,Return again when you feel,that you are ready.
A good fight.,Perhaps next time.
I will not be defeated this time!
Very well.
Oh，you’re back!,Here，have some tea!
On better days， the view from,up here is simply beautiful....
My highest duty is to serve,and protect Mistress Yuyuko.
Even still，it pains me to allow,our home to remain in such a,sorry state....
-- line not used --
Isn’t it beautiful?,Just the way it should be!
And right on time，too!,Look!
Ah，it’s been too long....
You have my deepest thanks，,Shanghai.,And Alice too，of course.
If you don’t mind，I’d like to,make sure all traces of the,corruption have been purged.
This will take just a moment，,then we can discuss matters,further.
It seems that you were very,thorough in your work.,I really am grateful.
No corruption remains，and,with my power restored it will,never gain a foothold again.
....Am I speaking differently?,My apologies，I tend to relax,while in my casualwear.
In any case，the stability of the,Area is no longer at risk，and,as for the intruders....
During their rampage，it seems,they fed on loose souls and,grew in power immensely.
As they are，the power needed,to overcome their unique nature,would devastate the Area.
Unfortunately，there is nothing,we can do now besides confine,them until they weaken.
If someone were to find a way,to safely release their souls，,however....
Well，it certainly saves some,time picking a reward from the,vaults，I suppose.
Well，you would know more,than I，I suppose.
It seems we owe you yet again.,After the souls they consumed,during their rampage....
The power we would have,needed to subdue them could,have devastated the Area.
How lucky that there was,someone nearby who could,counter their unique nature!
As thanks，please feel free to,help yourself to the contents,of the vaults.
Oh?,Was there something you,needed?
Challenge Yuyuko to a,NetBattle?
Ah，it’s been too long since,I’ve had the chance to stretch,my legs!
Our doors are always open,to you.
An error in the battle data,recorder?
My apologies，mundane,systems tend to have issues,analyzing my power.
Here.,To recognize a battle,well-fought.
It’s not every day that I get the,chance to go all out!
I should prepare something,special for Mistress Yuyuko....
Ah. Yes，thank you for cleaning,up the corruption， of course.
Now，what do make，what to,make....?
A battle well-fought.
